sentences.en: A warble for joy of lilac - time, returning in reminiscence.
sentences.cn: 唱一支深情的歌, 为这回忆中归来的丁香花季节的欢乐.

sentences.en: It's a pleasure to hear birds'warble in spring.
sentences.cn: 在春天里听鸟儿歌唱是一种乐趣.
米尔斯凑合着唱了几个音。

sentences.en: You may feel a little warble at the moment, but so have all the great singers.
sentences.cn: 有时,你可能觉得自己的歌声有些发颤, 但是所有伟大的歌唱家都有这种时刻.

words.tran_cn: 啭鸟；鸣鸟；用颤音歌唱的人

trans.tran_en: to sing with a high continuous but quickly changing sound, the way a bird does
